sercontent.com/23433306/102486170-9646c780-40a3-11eb-9a96-bba050510aab.gif)\r\n\r\nRun the same code in the terminal with IPython, work as expected.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"522\" alt=\"WX20201217-200728@2x\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23433306/102486257-ba0a0d80-40a3-11eb-85af-2d8c37cb44de.png\">\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom rich.progress import Progress\r\nfrom time import sleep\r\n\r\ndef test_rich():\r\n    print(\"before\")\r\n    sleep(0.5)\r\n    with Progress() as progress:\r\n        task = progress.add_task(\"task1\",total=10)\r\n        for job in range(10):\r\n            progress.console.print(f\"Working on job {job}\")\r\n            sleep(0.1)\r\n            progress.advance(task)\r\n\r\ntest_rich()\r\n\r\n```\r\n","closed_by":null,"performed_via_github_app":null}